title: Mu Wang Zhi Wang: You Du Zhan
synopsis: The 12th year of the Tai Calendar Luo Wuzi was ordered to build the Tomb of King Qin. Then he was given the title King of the Tomb. After building it, he became the King of the Tomb City and ruled over the Tomb of the World.
related_anime: ['Mu Wang Zhi Wang: Xuan Guan Si']
